National  defense  is  extremely  important,  and  we  should  spend
what we are spending there. But yes, in reality, you are looking at
about  $500  billion  for  national  defense,  and  about  $50  billion  for
education,  one  out  of  ten  dollars.  So,  if  someone  goes  to  work  for
