as  what  we  are  spending  in  many  other  areas.  That  is  part  of  our
national  defense,  and  for  some  reason,  we  can’t  get  that  through
the  heads  of  a  lot  of  folks  who  serve  in  Congress.  We  are  failing
at  that  as  well,  but  I  do  have  a  deep  and  abiding  concern  that
when  a  company  is  bought  by  a  Chinese  company,  like  Murray,
Inc.,  and  they  take  bankruptcy  after  giving  all  the  research  and
